726543f-a.title: Queens: Farmers Boulevard - Merrick Boulevard
726543f-a.text:
Farmers Boulevard, north from Merrick Boulevard. The old
house seen in the center of the view, on the east aide of the
Boulevard, was owned by W. R. Higbie in 1891 and by W.H.
Nostrand in 1918.
March 15, 1927
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS

726545f-b.title: Queens: Farmers Boulevard - Merrick Boulevard
726545f-b.text:
Farmers Boulevard, south from Merrick Boulevard, showing in
a set of two views Chas. Belr's Inn. View No. 2 shows the south
side of the Inn.
September 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
